event.title: ILISH FESTIVAL 2018
event.disclaimer: Restaurants are solely responsible for the service; availability and quality of the events including all or any cancellations/ modifications/ complaints.
event.description:
If rain sparks nostalgia so does the smell of fried hilsha. The silver beauty has sailed throughout the world with different names bearing the unique richness that has melted hearts since eternity. 
A fish so special that it has won the status of national fish for Bangladesh.
But no matter from which country,
Which state, every Bengali connects romantically with Hilsha, almost magically.
A fish so special, that Appyayan feels compelled to celebrate its taste with a entire new platter. 
Said that, we welcome you to our restaurant , at Aundh & Wakad, from 3rd to 19th Aug 2018, for the Grand Hilsha Festival.. Come, let's share goodness.

Cheers 
Team Apyayan
